<div class="app-card-container keep-away-nav">
    <div class="card">
        <h1>About Me</h1>

        <hr>
        
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <%= image_tag "newprofilepic.jpg", width: 450, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>
                
                <div class="skills">
                    <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
                        <div class="skill">
                            <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
                            <div class="progress">
                                <div 
                                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-danger"
                                  role="progressbar"
                                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                                  aria-valuemax="100"
                                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                                  ></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    <% end %>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <p>I am a Junior at Cottonwood High School who's dream is to become a great programmer. I am also an avid Marvel and Star Wars fan. I enjoy racing my junior dragster and I have one win, and two runner-ups, under my belt.</p>
                
                <p>I believe I have a responsibility to do good in this world. And I believe I can achieve this through coding.</p>
                
                <p>"With great power comes great responsibility." - Uncle Ben</p>
                
                <p>
                    <button
                      class="btn btn-outline-info"
                      type="button"
                      data-toggle="collapse"
                      data-target="#jobHistory"
                      aria-expanded="false"
                      aria-controler="jobHistory"
                    >
                        Job History ▼
                    </button>
                    <button
                      class="btn btn-outline-info"
                      type="button"
                      data-toggle="collapse"
                      data-target="#education"
                      aria-expanded="false"
                      aria-controler="education"
                    >
                        Education ▼
                    </button>
                </p>
                
                <p>
                    <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
                        <div class="card card-block">
                            None yet. 
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="collapse" id="education">
                        <div class="card card-block">
                            GTI
                        </div>
                        <div class="card card-block">
                            Code to success 2017
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>